description: Lists all AppConfig extension associations in the account. For more information about extensions and associations, see Extending workflows in the AppConfig User Guide.

nested_items.name: Items
nested_items.description: The list of extension associations. Each item represents an extension association to an application, environment, or configuration profile.

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: The extension association ID. This ID is used to call other ExtensionAssociation API actions such as GetExtensionAssociation or DeleteExtensionAssociation.

nested_items.name: ExtensionArn
nested_items.description: The system-generated Amazon Resource Name (ARN) for the extension.

nested_items.name: ResourceArn
nested_items.description: The ARNs of applications, configuration profiles, or environments defined in the association.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The token for the next set of items to return. Use this token to get the next set of results.
